{"tid":1165731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解越來越多香港人自認「港豬」","createTime":"2019-05-22T03:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T03:55:41.000Z","uid":107366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bde12db2b90c2fb1d692349c93cd4429df664855","tid":1165731,"uid":107366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"有時同身邊朋友提起「引渡逃犯條例」 佢地第一反應都係咁：「無睇呀，我港豬黎架嘛」唔緊要，咁你誼家睇啦好無？<br />\n<br />\n知你地無時間爬長文追POST，知你地生活已經好忙好煩好攰，無時間再理香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  知你或者曾經好關注香港，但係對於付出過嘅努力得唔到回報而好絕望（我都係），雖然咁講好老土，但係失敗一次唔代表要放棄繼續抵抗架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張圖講曬俾你知點解不得不反！今日唔關你事，難保將來唔關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMsPbw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMsPbw3.png&h=097ec717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/273942109482342/photos/a.275837955959424/1093006367575908/?type=3&amp;eid=ARDg4Q03FLQkLFlDwIM1zGqERN1VY3SWtAJS6IFUkpzIn0Rt64ADrDN8DdA2MC2LiscJlF-aOOeB_6fG&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARD_ItmfxsHTWOVRslD3z-qNimI6jJDvzTUSF9EMZUwWaM24gZbp3aY_kGSSwtIJALd1xIC8j2QWkFS2WobbDRgf37idTaC-UA-wDK-K0t6qyw6In1CKn2_yxHn_cxex5dhvdi4EPpXo6rE65qiVtYrTbEsKl5AqC8fiTxR3WFKwJK9n7G_a3v6pBulUcTG_d0XadHbBgtKkjLXRiSH6rc03VcRJB3pL_BhuKfI5ON6Q5Zk8tC9j2sgoxqHNByL8uLyS1fTt_2aAt60XkImTecIxEFAuvhVt7m_s6620YYvD6EV2TuVuvlRg4YwF1b4CJ7F3rZj-f_p8O3rT-92FTfFFem83XrDJCnC2hAjGR1mtv2Q&amp;__tn__=EEHH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F273942109482342%2Fphotos%2Fa.275837955959424%2F1093006367575908%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26eid%3DARDg4Q03FLQkLFlDwIM1zGqERN1VY3SWtAJS6IFUkpzIn0Rt64ADrDN8DdA2MC2LiscJlF-aOOeB_6fG%26__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARD_ItmfxsHTWOVRslD3z-qNimI6jJDvzTUSF9EMZUwWaM24gZbp3aY_kGSSwtIJALd1xIC8j2QWkFS2WobbDRgf37idTaC-UA-wDK-K0t6qyw6In1CKn2_yxHn_cxex5dhvdi4EPpXo6rE65qiVtYrTbEsKl5AqC8fiTxR3WFKwJK9n7G_a3v6pBulUcTG_d0XadHbBgtKkjLXRiSH6